The data I will be evaluating comes from a climate station at Chicagos Midway airport located on the south side of Chicago, Illinois. This weather station has been recording various forms of climate data since Februrary 29th, 1928, all the ay to December 11th, 2019. It has a 96% data ccoverage and an elevation of 189 feet.

Information on Chicago: location, type of climate historically, communities and spcies, there.

shytown$Month = format(as.Date(shytown$NewDate), format = "%m")
shytown$Year = format(shytown$NewDate, format="%Y")

MonthlyTMAXMean = aggregate(TMAX ~ Month + Year, shytown, mean)
MonthlyTMAXMean$YEAR = as.numeric(MonthlyTMAXMean$Year)
MonthlyTMAXMean$MONTH = as.numeric(MonthlyTMAXMean$Month)

str(MonthlyTMAXMean)
